title: Red Beans and Rice NOLA style
date: 2022-04-06
category: main
tags: dry beans, instant pot, cajun
---

Prep time: 15 mins
Cook time: 50 mins
Total time: 1+ hr

Serves: 6-8

## Ingredients
* smoked sausage, sliced (plus tablespoon oil)
* 1/4 stick butter (2 tbsp)
* 2-3 c. onions, celery, green bell pepper, parsley, 1 clove garlic
* 1 pound red kidney beans
* 6 c. water
* bay leaf
* cajun seasoning, salt & pepper to taste
* Hot cooked white rice

## Instructions
1. rinse/sort beans
2. saute sliced sausage, reserve
3. Add butter & veges blend. Cook till onions are soft/clear
4. Add beans, water, bay leaf, half of sausage
5. pressure cook for 40 min
6. mash beans to creamy. Add seasonings
7. Serve over hot cooked rice with the reserved sausage

[Source: Camellia Brand](https://www.camelliabrand.com/recipes/instant-pot-new-orleans-style-red-beans-and-rice/)
